	<div class="story-page" id="story-block-1">
		<p>This is where we find ourselves. A new cider house, trying to establish its roots within the Niagara Region. Filled with ambition and a sense of adventure, Malus Cider House was born from a passion for the fruits of the land and the perseverance of a dream!</p>
	
		<p><%= image_tag("niagara-on-the-lake.jpg", :alt => "Niagara-on-the-Lake", :class => "about-image", :id => "about-image-1") %>
		At Malus Cider House, the first step in thinking outside of the box is our world-famous (Well… someday… for now we will just say our personal favorite and soon to be yours) our - <span class="em-text">HOPPED CIDER</span>. Made from local apples, our hopped cider is accompanied be a complimenting citrus note… and that is all we will tell you for now! There is only one way for you to find out if your like it, so check out the <%= link_to "Store", "/charges/new", :class => "red-link" %> and <%= link_to "Locations", "/contact", :class => "red-link" %> pages to find our hopped cider and enjoy!</p>

		<p>On another note (no pun intended), to help us to help you to enjoy your free, spare, alone time, happy hour, your cider o’clock. Whenever and wherever that may be, and whatever adventure that you decide to bring us on, we would love to hear from you on our <%= link_to "Blog", "/articles", :class => "red-link"  %>. </p>

		<p style="text-align: center">Cheers!</p>
